title: FULT Makes Bullish Cross Above Critical Moving Average - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of Fulton Financial Corp. (Symbol: FULT) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $16.30, changing hands as high as $16.42 per share. Fulton Financial Corp. shares are currently trading up about 0.6% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of FULT shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, FULT's low point in its 52 week range is $14.38 per share, with $17.95 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $16.30.
